The '''Moldavian Cycling Federation''' ({{lang-ro|Federaţia de Ciclism a Republicii Moldova}}), abbreviated to '''FCM''', is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Moldova]].

The FCMis a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]].

