The '''Volta ao Distrito de Santarém''' {{pt icon}} (Tour of Santarém District) is a [[road bicycle racing]] stage race held annually in the [[Santarém (district)|District of Santárem]], Portugal. Since 2006, it has been organised as a 2.1 event on the [[UCI Europe Tour]].

